Table 18.  Supplemental data for State governments, 1996
Note:  "Estimated population" represents resident U.S. population (50 states excluding the District of Columbia)
from the Bureau of the Census, Current Population Reports, July 1996.
The October 1995 employment and payrolls data were used for both
1995 and 1996 Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts.
a/ "Personal income" is from the U.S. Department of Commerce, Survey of Current Business, August 1996.
b/ "Total general expenditure" excludes utilities, State-operated liquor stores, and insurance trust benefits.
c/ "General functions only" FTE excludes utilities, and State-operated liquor stores.
